## Transformation Details

### Rebranding
- Old Name: ${OLD_PROJECT_NAME_CAMELCASE} / ${OLD_PROJECT_NAME_KEBAB}
- New Name: ${NEW_PROJECT_NAME_CAMELCASE} / ${NEW_PROJECT_NAME_KEBAB}
- Files Modified: $(wc -l < ../security-reports/rebranded-files.txt)

